radiographic_examinations.findings: Complete conduction block proximal to the head of the fibula of the right peroneal nerve, a partial conduction block of the left ulnar nerve between the axilla and elbow, and a suspected partial motor conduction block of the left peroneal nerve distal of the head of the fibula.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: Disease progression observed with complete conduction block of the right peroneal and left ulnar nerve and partial conduction block of the left peroneal nerve.
